# CODEOWNERS — LQ.AI
# ============================================================
# Path-based reviewer assignments. The most recent matching
# pattern takes precedence; later patterns override earlier ones.
#
# At launch, the @legalquants/maintainers team handles all
# default reviews. As the project grows and specialized teams
# stand up (security, compliance, practicing-attorneys), this
# file is updated to route reviews appropriately.
#
# References:
# - PR review process: ../CONTRIBUTING.md#pull-request-process
# - Skill review process: ../skills/CONTRIBUTING.md
# ============================================================

# Default — all changes require maintainer review
*                              @legalquants/maintainers

# ---------- Repository-level governance ----------
/LICENSE                       @legalquants/maintainers
/CODE_OF_CONDUCT.md            @legalquants/maintainers
/CONTRIBUTING.md               @legalquants/maintainers
/SECURITY.md                   @legalquants/maintainers @legalquants/security
/.github/CODEOWNERS            @legalquants/maintainers

# ---------- Security-sensitive paths ----------
# Inference Gateway holds the security boundary; changes here
# require security review in addition to maintainer review.
/gateway/                      @legalquants/maintainers @legalquants/security
/docs/security/                @legalquants/security @legalquants/maintainers
/.github/workflows/            @legalquants/maintainers @legalquants/security

# ---------- Compliance documentation ----------
# Compliance Alignment Pack mappings affect procurement posture;
# changes require counsel + maintainer review.
/docs/compliance/              @legalquants/counsel @legalquants/maintainers
/docs/procurement/             @legalquants/counsel @legalquants/maintainers

# ---------- Skills (legal substance) ----------
# Skills containing legal substance require attorney review
# in addition to maintainer review. See skills/CONTRIBUTING.md
# for the attestation and review process.
/skills/                       @legalquants/maintainers @legalquants/practicing-attorneys
/skills/CONTRIBUTING.md        @legalquants/maintainers @legalquants/practicing-attorneys

# ---------- Canonical specification ----------
# PRD changes affect every downstream artifact; require
# maintainer review by default.
/docs/PRD.md                   @legalquants/maintainers
/docs/architecture.md          @legalquants/maintainers
/docs/skill-authoring-guide.md @legalquants/maintainers @legalquants/practicing-attorneys
